EXTENSION_SEED_KIND

static final java.lang.String EXTENSION_SEED_KIND
Change event extension constant used in stream component events which indicate the kind of seed used for a component addition/replacement. Expected values would include: IWorkspace#ITEM_TYPE.getName() and IBaseline#ITEM_TYPE.getName() If the extension is not set, it means that no seed was provided.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

EXTENSION_SEED_ID

static final java.lang.String EXTENSION_SEED_ID
Change event extension constant used in stream component events which indicate the kind of seed used for a component addition/replacement. Expected values would include: IWorkspace#ITEM_TYPE.getName() and IBaseline#ITEM_TYPE.getName() If the extension is not set, it means that no seed was provided.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

EXTENSION_ATTRIBUTE_NAME

static final java.lang.String EXTENSION_ATTRIBUTE_NAME
Change event extension constant used in stream events which indicate a stream property has changed. Valid values include: IWorkspace.NAME_PROPERTY IWorkspace.DESCRIPTION_PROPERTY Workspace.FLOWS_PROPERTY
